Release 0.1.22: labels toggle switch, ADARV credit, team authors

- Replace the labels checkbox with a sliding on/off toggle switch (ADARV
  navy when on, grey when off) plus a live On/Off status label.
- Add a credit caption at the bottom of the map ("Interactive spot maps
  for India - created by ADARV"), included in PNG/PDF exports.
- Credit the ADARV team: add all members to pyproject authors/maintainers
  (shown on PyPI), a Team section in the README, and a new AUTHORS.md.
- Update copyright holder to ADARV (LICENSE + README).
- Bump version 0.1.20 -> 0.1.22.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
